=head2 Logical Methods

=over 4

=item C<PMC *logical_or(PMC *value, PMC *dest)>

Returns the result of the logical C<OR> of C<SELF> and C<value>, i.e. returns
C<SELF> it is true or C<value>: C<dest> is alway ignored.

